   "stance": "contradicts",
   "quote": "This requirement is open only to those Electrical & Electronic Products Supply Arrangement Holders who qualified under Stream two (2) for services in the National Capital Region for the following category: 1. Stream two (2) – Electronic Products Following SA Holders have been invited to submit a proposal"
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.merx.com/public/supplier/solicitations/notice/22784996660/abstract",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "Shared Services Canada (SSC) has a requirement for Raritan Power Distribution Units and Vertiv Racks, or equivalent"
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.it-beschaffung.ch/564/beschaffung-von-stromverteilereinheiten-pdu",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "Marktabklärungen zeigten, dass nur eine Firma PDU anbieten kann... Die Vergabe an die Firma Riedo Networks AG erfolgt somit freihändig"
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.utahbids.net/bid-result/enlogic_power_distribution_units-14182081",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "Intellivex Data Center Solutions is the apparent low bidder on the University of Utah - Purchasing's Enlogic Power Distribution Units solicitation, with a low bid of $129,775.09 USD"
  },
  {
   "url": "https://prospeo.io/s/serviceable-obtainable-market",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "SOM is the revenue you can realistically capture in 1-3 years. Not a fantasy percentage of SAM."
  },
  {
